body:
@mcmire this is a good point! 
In metamask-mobile's Engine.js we just instantiate the core KeyringController (`@metamask/keyring-controller`) and interact with the underlying eth-keyring-controller through it.

On the other hand, on metamask-extension, we instantiate eth-keyring-controller directly and interact with it, duplicating the logic that is now in the core's KeyringController
